NAME: Part
DOC: expr[[i]] or Part[expr,i] gives the ith part of expr. expr[[-i]] counts from the end. expr[[i,j,...]] or Part[expr,i,j,...] is equivalent to expr[[i]][[j]].... expr[[{i1,i2,...}]] gives a list of the parts i1, i2, ... of expr. expr[[m;;n]] gives parts m through n. expr[[m;;n;;s]] gives parts m through n in steps of s.
